{
  "id": "61e91b38e9993c001e7e725a",
  "title": "(2.3.1.1) Large task of writing a book",
  "created": 1548921433,
  "updated": 1553660976,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15ab",
      "text": "(2.3.1.1) Large task of writing a book",
      "created": 1548921433,
      "updated": 1553660976,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15ac",
      "text": "Right now I am doing an intellectual production task: \"[writing a book].\" *1",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923313,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15ad",
      "text": "This task is also too big to estimate time. ",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15ae",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548923326,
      "updated": 1548923330,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15af",
      "text": "If we regard writing as a big task, writing motivation is difficult to keep.",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b0",
      "text": "Therefore it is common to divide the task into each chapter and set the deadline for each chapter.",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b1",
      "text": "However, the task of writing one chapter is still too large. I can not finish it in 4 hours. *18",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b2",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923353,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b3",
      "text": "To motivate this big task \"writing a book,\" I broke down the task into the following three phases.",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923539,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b4",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b5",
      "text": "  1: Make notes of the idea as [fusen]s. *2",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b6",
      "text": "  2: Rearrange fusens and organize a composition",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b7",
      "text": "  3: Make a manuscript based on the composition",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923511,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b8",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548923335,
      "updated": 1548923338,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15b9",
      "text": "A good point of this method is, we can do the first phase even in fractional time. For example, you can make notes even in a commuter train.",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15ba",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15bb",
      "text": "Writing a book from nothing is a very heavy task. However, if there are hundreds of fusens, organizing and converting them into sentences is not such a heavy task. I explain the method in detail in Chapter 5.",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923533,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15bc",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15bd",
      "text": "\t*1: For this English version, I am doing \"[translating a book into English].\"",
      "created": 1548923341,
      "updated": 1548923342,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15be",
      "text": "\t*2: fusen = Small piece of paper with weak glue (in Japanese),  Post-it (Registered trademark of 3M), or Sticky (in American English)",
      "created": 1548923341,
      "updated": 1548923343,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15bf",
      "text": "　*18 I already spent more than 4 hours",
      "created": 1548923123,
      "updated": 1548923123,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e00005f15c0",
      "text": "[en.icon]",
      "created": 1553660976,
      "updated": 1553660976,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    }
  ]
}